  "title": "ASSISTANT MANAGER",
  "description": "<p>Create and implement effective marketing strategies to introduce and promote new products across both digital and traditional platforms.</p><p>Monitor and motivate the sales team to meet and exceed individual and team sales targets through strategic marketing support and campaign alignment.</p><p>Plan, organize, and oversee promotional activities and marketing events, ensuring smooth coordination of logistics, staffing, and on-site execution.</p><p>Guide and mentor Marketing Associates, providing clear direction, hands-on training, and regular performance feedback to build a high-performing team.</p><p>Review current marketing initiatives, identify areas for improvement, and implement cost-effective solutions within budget constraints.</p><p>Conduct market research to identify potential untapped markets and develop actionable plans to successfully enter and grow within those segments.</p><p>Willingness to work night shift and split shift.</p><p>Willingness to work extra hours or weekend if needed.</p>",
